> Hi all - What, if any components from an H case sp 1500 with an alternator 
> can be fitted on a new 1600 dp longblock?  

Hi Don,
Everything except the SP intake manifold and top head tin.  We highly suggest 
for a daily driver bus engine of using a doghouse shroud and its larger fan 
rather than the earlier type shroud.
